#: ../../docs/changelog.rst:23 2e4a7ac9bb9a4d89a37f37969f2028f9
msgid ""
"**Legacy token authentication removed** — "
"``BrokerBuilder.UseAuthentication(string)``, ``BrokerOptions.AuthToken``,"
" ``ClientOptions.AuthToken``, ``BrokerOptions.EnableAuthentication``, and"
" the Connect handshake ``authToken`` header path are removed. Use "
"``UseAuthorization()`` with ``Username`` and ``Password`` on the client."
msgstr ""
"**Удалена устаревшая аутентификация по токену** — удалены "
"``BrokerBuilder.UseAuthentication(string)``, ``BrokerOptions.AuthToken``, "
"``ClientOptions.AuthToken``, ``BrokerOptions.EnableAuthentication``, а "
"также путь заголовка ``authToken`` в команде Connect. Используйте "
"``UseAuthorization()`` с ``Username`` и ``Password`` на клиенте."

#: ../../docs/changelog.rst:24 d3717e286b4c4d05967116882886dbd0
msgid ""
"**Removed types** — ``IAuthenticationService`` and "
"``TokenAuthenticationService``."
msgstr ""
"**Удалённые типы** — ``IAuthenticationService`` и "
"``TokenAuthenticationService``."

